OL,3,CArne Slot still believes he has
OL,4,Csupport of Liverpool fans
OL,6,FArne Slot insists he feels the
OL,7,F"complete support" of the Liverpool FC
OL,8,Fhierarchy as he comes under growing
OL,9,Fpressure following three consecutive
OL,10,Fdefeats.
OL,12,FAfter seeing their FA Cup campaign end
OL,13,Fin a 4-0 quarter-final loss to
OL,14,FManchester City, Liverpool's Champions
OL,15,FLeague hopes hang by a thread
OL,16,Ffollowing Wednesday's 2-0 quarter-
OL,17,Ffinal first leg loss to Paris St
OL,18,FGermain.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@RO]
