OL,3,CArne Slot still believes he has
OL,4,Csupport of Liverpool fans
OL,6,FA 2-1 loss at Brighton in their last
OL,7,Fleague outing left the defending
OL,8,Fchampions fifth, scrapping for
OL,9,FChampions League qualification and
OL,10,Ftalk that Slot is fighting for his
OL,11,Fjob, a year on from winning the
OL,12,FPremier League, has grown around
OL,13,FAnfield.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
