PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775833867
OL,3,CArne Slot still believes he has
OL,4,Csupport of Liverpool fans
OL,6,F"I'm repeating myself a lot but I've
OL,7,Fsaid many times I feel a lot of
OL,8,Fsupport, not only from the owners and
OL,9,Ffrom Richard (Hughes, Sporting
OL,10,FDirector) and Michael (Edwards, Chief
OL,11,FExecutive), I feel a lot of support
OL,12,Ffrom them as well," Slot said ahead of
OL,13,FSaturday's match against Fulham.
OL,15,F"But as weird as it might sound, I
OL,16,Falso feel the support of the fans. We
OL,17,Fwere going out in Paris, when the
OL,18,Fplayers went out for the warm-up and
OL,19,Fthe fans, after a 4-0 loss,
OL,20,Fimmediately start singing 'We love
OL,21,Fyou, Liverpool'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@NpmrD@IpnrD@WpmsD@JpntD@SO]wD@
OL,26,AAOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775833867
OL,3,CArne Slot still believes he has
OL,4,Csupport of Liverpool fans
OL,6,F"And after we were - I think it's fair
OL,7,Fto say - outplayed over 90 minutes, we
OL,8,Fwent to the away end and they were
OL,9,Fstill singing for us and clapping for
OL,10,Fus so that support I've felt that
OL,11,Fconstantly.
OL,13,F"I've said many times the club knows
OL,14,Fwhich period of time we are in and in
OL,15,Fthe meantime I feel complete support."
OL,17,FSlot's comments about fan backing came
OL,18,Fon the eve of planned protests against
OL,19,Fthe club's decision to raise ticket
OL,20,Fprices for the next three years in
OL,21,Fline with inflation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
