CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775833867
OL,3,CArne Slot still believes he has
OL,4,Csupport of Liverpool fans
OL,6,FAmid fears that the club's hardcore
OL,7,Fsupport risks being priced out, Slot
OL,8,Fwas asked about the importance of
OL,9,Fthose in the stands.
OL,11,F"It's not only when we go through
OL,12,Ftough times," he said. "I think
OL,13,FAnfield has shown in history and also
OL,14,Fsince I'm here how important these
OL,15,Ffans are for us.
OL,17,F"When we played against Galatasaray,
OL,18,Fwe had a tough away game where their
OL,19,Ffans were really loud, but then
OL,20,FAnfield showed what being loud really
OL,21,Fis.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@MO]tD@XOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775833867
OL,3,CArne Slot still believes he has
OL,4,Csupport of Liverpool fans
OL,6,F"They helped us through that game and
OL,7,FI can come up with so many examples
OL,8,FI've been part of and in the history
OL,9,Fof this club.
OL,11,F"That is what makes it feel special...
OL,12,Fwe've always felt that support and
OL,13,FI've always felt that support in good
OL,14,Fand in bad times.
OL,16,F"I hope even though there are protests
OL,17,Fthat the fans can be as helpful as
OL,18,Fthey have always been for us this
OL,19,Fseason and last year."
OL,26,@sD@AOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
