OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775833867
OL,3,CArne Slot still believes he has
OL,4,Csupport of Liverpool fans
OL,6,FSlot also paid tribute to left-back
OL,7,FAndy Robertson, who announced on 9
OL,8,FApril he will leave Liverpool in the
OL,9,Fsummer after nine seasons in which he
OL,10,Fwon two Premier League titles, the
OL,11,FChampions League, FA Cup and two
OL,12,FLeague Cups among a string of honours.
OL,14,F"He has had many great seasons here as
OL,15,Fa player, but I think people got to
OL,16,Fknow him as a great person as well..."
OL,17,FSlot said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
