PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1775833867
OL,3,CArne Slot still believes he has
OL,4,Csupport of Liverpool fans
OL,6,F"He's won everything over here, served
OL,7,Fthis club for so many years, really
OL,8,Floves this club. It's been a great
OL,9,Fnine years but I think also we saw
OL,10,Fthis season he didn't play as much as
OL,11,Fhe was used to.
OL,13,F"Still a lot but not as much as he was
OL,14,Fused to and as a result of that he's
OL,15,Fleaving."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@IO]
